<h2>What is this?</h2>
<p>This is the screen that enables you to look at assignments that are pertinent to you.  &quot;Assignments&quot; are used by the system to keep track of what is due, when, and by whom.  Someone (a teacher, usually) will have made the assignments that you will see.  The select drop box below has a list of the groups that you belong to.  Rubrics, documents, and evaluation vectors can be associated with assignments. </p>

<h2>What do I do with it?</h2>
<p>  Choose the group whose assignments you wish to view and then press the &quot;Show Assignments&quot; button.</p>
[% IF AddLink %]
<p>To add a new assignment, select the &quot;add an assignment&quot; link below.</p>
[% END %]
